                                    <i class="fa fa-eye-slash" aria-hidden="true"></i> Privacy
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    No JavaScript is used. No IP addresses of user accounts are stored. All vendors have PGP. The database is always encrypted through the use of homomorphic encryption. All files are served from our server, no third parties. View our <a href="/privacy/">privacy policy</a>.
                                </p>
