                                <p class="lead">
                                    <i class="fa fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i> Multisig escrow
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    2-of-3 multisignature is available to buyers that wish to use it for Bitcoin. If not the marketplace will form a 2-of-2 with the vendor. Monero and Zcash use a direct deposit as escrow. Every order has a unique currency address, meaning there are no account deposits.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="column is-third">
                                <p class="lead">
                                    <i class="fa fa-money" aria-hidden="true"></i> Financial
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    The marketplace is available in Bitcoin, Monero, and Zcash. You can also make money from commissions with users that sign up with your code. Vendors are able to upload a HD wallet master public key to create unique bitcoin addresses for each transaction.
                                </p>
